				<cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Commodity Exchange Act/s:2/ss:h/p:7/sp:A">section 2(h)(7)(A)</cato:entity-ref> or <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Commodity Exchange Act/s:2/ss:h/p:7/sp:D">2(h)(7)(D)</cato:entity-ref>, or an exemption issued under
