			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="End-User Protection Act of 2014/s:7/ss:c/p:1" proposed="true">paragraph (1)</cato:entity-ref> shall apply solely to changes to rules and regulations, or
